  "body": "<p>It's been busy around here - there's a fun announcement coming on Thursday! It's something <a href=\"http://kellypurkey.typepad.com/\">Kelly</a> &amp; I have been working on for months and months and are extremely excited about sharing with all of you. Since I love snapping photos of my process (these are all taken with my iPhone), I thought I would share with you how this layout came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/aaa97f0ed1d2b51d.jpg?v=1782533263\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f0e068ec4080601d.jpg?v=1782533266\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>By cutting the squares in half, a perfectly sized triangle is made!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"3c-20140309-065916.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/25dd3cfdecbd47e3.jpg?v=1782533268\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3d-20140309-065928.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a4c608349190ac5b.jpg?v=1782533271\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3e-20140309-065938.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e67ec50cd8d93def.jpg?v=1782533274\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3f-20140309-065950.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9e5016b5b224b158.jpg?v=1782533276\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3g-20140309-070014.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f87a07c49ced1f60.jpg?v=1782533280\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3h-20140309-070027.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bb76a4ee9728d2bc.jpg?v=1782533282\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3i-20140309-070054.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f9a70143679c8ab8.jpg?v=1782533285\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3j-20140309-070108.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/000525dfe276a0a4.jpg?v=1782533288\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3k-we-are-the-lucky-ones.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/036fc14155ba47e9.jpg?v=1782533291\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Shop for our latest products online at Two Peas In A Bucket and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=simon%20home%20page&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom\">Simon Says Stamp</a> and <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/search?query=amy%20tangerine\">HSN</a>!</p>"
